# comment-only-in-prefix-block

## Input

```
s {
  # comment1
  # comment2
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..32
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..32
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "s"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    COMMENT@6..16
      SHARP@6..7 "#"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      WORD@8..16 "comment1"
    NEWLINE@16..17 "\n"
    SPACE@17..19 "  "
    COMMENT@19..29
      SHARP@19..20 "#"
      SPACE@20..21 " "
      WORD@21..29 "comment2"
    NEWLINE@29..30 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@30..31 "}"
    NEWLINE@31..32 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "s",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{",
            items: [],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@30..31 "}",
        },
    ],
}
